data.description: The Cypress Plan- built by Ben Stout is a beautiful 4 bedroom, 2 1/2 bath home located in a quiet neighborhood. Walk into your new home that opens up to family room, dining, and large kitchen. All bedrooms are located on the second floor of the home. Owners Suite includes His/Her walk in closets, dual vanities, garden tub, and separate shower. Laundry is located on the second floor. Stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, and more! Covered back patio and two car garage. Schedule your showing today!
